title: Volleyball roundup: Clyde wins
text:

Clyde 3, Lake 0 
Clyde (12-11) needed only three games in a Sectional Semifinal win, 25-8, 25-13, 25-14 at home. Heidi Marshall had eight digs and six kills while Jenna Hoppe had 16 digs. Morgan Bannister had 27 assists. 
Calvert 3, Lakota 0 
Lakota (5-17) lost in three games in Sectional play, 25-23, 25-15, 25-23 at Calvert. Bree Long-Meyer had 23 digs, nine kills and four aces while Aubrey Bickford had 16 assists and three aces. Alexis Kirkpatrick had 12 kills. 
Clear Fork 3 Oak Harbor 2 
Oak Harbor lost in five games, 25-23, 25-23, 11-25, 21-25, 17-15 in Sectional tournament play. No individual statistics were provided. Read or Share this story: http://ohne.ws/1LJNXQ5 TOP VIDEOS
